<i>Mother Sun, we greet you,</i>

54:21.253 --> 54:24.888
and are thankful for
the sweetness of the Earth.

54:24.923 --> 54:29.142
<i>The new day brings new hope.</i>

54:29.178 --> 54:31.478
<i>The lives we've led,</i>

54:31.513 --> 54:34.648
<i>the lives we've yet to lead.</i>

54:34.683 --> 54:36.983
<i>New day,</i>

54:37.019 --> 54:39.986
<i>new ideas,</i>

54:40.022 --> 54:41.988
<i>a new you.</i>

